data.description: If you're looking for a beautiful home in a peaceful location, check out this 2 year old, 4 bedroom, 2 bath house located in the Caledonia school district. Step inside where you will find a split floor plan with open concept living that incorporates a beautiful kitchen equipped with crisp white double stacked cabinetry, oversized peninsula, trellis-patterned backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. This home has the works with many highly sought after features that include granite throughout, luxury vinyl plank flooring, neutral paint colors, as well as a sparkling inground swimming pool, 30x30 Shop, and sits on an expansive 3.2 ac lot.
